body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation

2. Polarity Verif.
3. Burden
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

3. Burden
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

## Activities

1. Pump-Fan Op.
2. Oil Flow Verif.
3. Temp. Control

## Activities

1. Moist. Content
2. Dielec. Strength
3. Acidity

document.title: Circuit Breaker
document.description: Maintenance activities for Circuit Breaker in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation

# Contactor

## Activities

1. Pickup-Dropout
2. Contact Resist.
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Mech. Endurance

# Directional OC

## Activities

1. Discrimination
2. Pickup
3. Timing

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Ins. Resist.

document.description: Maintenance activities for Lockout Relay in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Lockout Relay

## Activities

1. Func. Trip-Reset
2. Contact Resist.
3. Coil Pickup

document.title: Motor Prot.
document.description: Maintenance activities for Motor Prot. in HV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Motor Prot.

## Activities

1. Starting Time
2. Stall Prot.
3. Thermal OL
4. Unbal./Ph Loss

# Overcurrent

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Char. Curve
4. Ins. Resist.

body.raw:
# Voltage Transformer

## Activities

1. Ratio
2. Polarity Verif.
3. Burden
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Sat. Curve

body.raw:
# SCADA

## Activities

1. Point-to-Point Communication
2. Time Synchronization
3. Failover Redundancy
4. Alarm-Trip Integration

## Activities

body.raw:
# Distribution Board

## Activities

1. Ins. Resist.
2. Busbar Tightness
3. Volt. Stability
4. Phase Seq. Verif.
5. Func. Breaker-RCD Coord.

2. Load Bal. Verif.
3. Func. MCB-RCD Op.

# MCCB

## Activities

1. Trip Time SC-OL
2. Ins. Resist.
3. Contact Resist.
4. Mech. Operation

document.description: Maintenance activities for Circuit Breaker in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Circuit Breaker

## Activities

1. Contact Resist.
2. Timing Open-Close
3. Ins. Resist.
4. Coil Pickup
5. SF6 Gas Press.-Purity
6. Vacuum Integrity
7. Mech. Operation

document.description: Maintenance activities for Differential in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Differential

## Activities

1. Rat/Ph Angle
2. Slope Char.
3. Harm. Restr.
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Functional

2. Timing

# General

## Activities

1. Sec. Injection
2. Pri. Injection
3. Settings Verif.
4. Communication
5. Contact Resist.

document.title: Overcurrent
document.description: Maintenance activities for Overcurrent in MV SWGR system

body.raw:
# Overcurrent

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Char. Curve
4. Ins. Resist.
5. Burden

# Control Panel

## Activities

1. Alarm Indic.
2. Trip Circuit
3. Volt. Regulation

# Distance

## Activities

1. Impedance
2. Zone Timing
3. Directional
4. Polarization

## Activities

1. Pickup
2. Timing
3. Insulation Resistance
